{"tid":1107731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 濟南藥廠燒焊點著隔熱物質　十名工人因毒煙霧窒息亡","createTime":"2019-04-15T12:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T13:24:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28950a3daaf9e3f9904b533a2f87797c174cbb7e","tid":1107731,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:39:44.000Z","msg":"濟南市一間製藥廠發生工業意外，10人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n下午三時許，當地的齊魯天和惠世制藥有限公司的冷凍庫，在進行管道改造時，因電燒焊火花，點著低溫傳熱物質產生煙霧，在現場工作的10名工人，8人當場窒息死亡，其餘2人搶救過程中不治，另外12名救援人員受傷，無生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，經環保部門檢測，意外對周邊環境未造成影響，當局正調查事故起因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453006-20190415.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453006-20190415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUamvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=8bf96273\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453006-20190415.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a24d2ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453006-20190415.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"09a75a3146dc98a6408d914cadcf9fac5a3402fd","tid":1107731,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02da8cff3dda45f585d7a0dea91890005e3dd1ba","tid":1107731,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"無害jpg<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意外對周邊環境未造成影響<br />\n意外對周邊環境未造成影響"},{"pid":"e90eb51fe6a9680bd45276a9b7f7d6e5c47d5be0","tid":1107731,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T12:42:46.000Z","msg":"點解有毒煙都唔走？"},{"pid":"590fba22388bf4acea90eda6222d82fa820fc588","tid":1107731,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"防火唔防毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm